//Credits Credits Sam Law - App Creator Mark Becker - App Creator
//About About the Trail RAGBRAI is a seven day biking event in which participants bike across the entire state of Iowa. RAGBRAI will run for its 46th time in the upcoming summer. It is the oldest, largest, and longest recreational bike touring event in the world. It is an amazing journey and we would recommend riding it in real life!
//Choose Difficulty Many kinds of people ride RAGBRAI every year. You can be: 1. A College Student 2. An Accountant 3. A Retired Person 4. Find out the difference between characters
//Difference between Characters The Difference of Characters 1. Picking a college student will give you a lot of energy to start the game, but not very much money. 2. Picking an accountant will give you a balanced supply of energy and money. 3. Picking a retired person will give you more money but less energy.
//Pick A Character Name What is the Name of your Character?
//Buy Supplies Casey\'s General Store Amount You Have: $ Energy Level: Food $1 Helmet $30 Spare Part $50 Quantity Buy Supplies Learn About Products Continue on the Trail
//Learn About Products 1. Buying food will replenish energy instantly depending on how much you buy. One food object will give you one energy. 2. Buying a helmet will prevent injuries from accidents. Injuries can slow you down or even cause you to not complete the RAGBRAI trail. 3. Buying spare parts can solve all kinds of problems. You will want to have spare parts just in case you have problems with your bike.
